{
  "id": "RAW_10ebd7",
  "title": "开源 SOTA：阶跃发布端到端语音大模型 Step-Audio 2 mini！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTM5NTg2OA==&mid=2247506011&idx=1&sn=d55346205d02685da9ad06e8a1025d4d",
  "date": "2025-09-01 09:39:00",
  "author": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "siteName": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=66976216&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0LDJQiaWfxzk9FfRXt0XUMRQdWOLavasonC2so40le8mjHLYfOeoqEU7xIF7Uy1Jgv9OHYJZKYVlqT9Tick7Dgiaw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 8px 8px 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大家好，</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">今天阶跃星辰正式发布</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">最强开源端到端语音大模型&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">Step-Audio 2 mini，该模型在多个国际基准</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">测试集</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">上取得 SOTA 成绩</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 8px 8px 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它将语音理解、音频推理与生成统一建模，在音频理解、语音识别、跨语种翻译、情感与副语言解析、语音对话等任务中表现突出，并率先支持语音原生的 Tool Calling 能力，可实现联网搜索等操作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一句话总结，Step-Audio 2 mini “</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">听得</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">清楚</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">、想得明白、说得自然</span></span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">”。模型现已上线 GitHub、</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ModelScope</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;等平台，欢迎大家下载、试用并反馈。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:small;min-height:1.5em !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-color:rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.05);outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;text-indent:0px;border-left:10px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.075);font-family:ExtraLight-0;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:2px 6px 2px 10px !important;margin:10px 16px 10px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:1px !important;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2 !important;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(143, 149, 158);visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;\">GitHub：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(120, 172, 254);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/stepfun-ai/Step-Audio2\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/stepfun-ai/Step-Audio2</a></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(143, 149, 158);font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;\">Hugging Face：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(120, 172, 254);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/stepfun-ai/Step-Audio-2-mini\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/stepfun-ai/Step-Audio-2-mini</a></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(143, 149, 158);font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;\">ModelScope：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(120, 172, 254);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://www.modelscope.cn/models/stepfun-ai/Step-Audio-2-mini\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.modelscope.cn/models/stepfun-ai/Step-Audio-2-mini</a></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 40px 8px 32px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;\">&nbsp;性能 SOTA&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-Audio 2 mini 在多个关键基准测试中取得 SOTA 成绩，在音频理解、语音识别、翻译和对话场景中表现突出，综合性能超越 Qwen-Omni 、Kimi-Audio 在内的所有开源端到端语音模型，并在大部分任务上超越 GPT-4o Audio。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100002791\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4980769230769231\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"288\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f32e954c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznjXuFh1FL7hJ1kOQrOmKynNUy4pAE31Fibr1H0ttHkNNqP0wOqTAY0Liaick5AVeCib5U5rf3C0ARSzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在通用多模态音频理解测试集 MMAU 上，Step-Audio 2 mini 以 73.2 的得分位列开源端到端语音模型榜首；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在衡量口语对话能力的 URO Bench 上， Step-Audio 2 mini 在基础与专业赛道均拿下开源端到端语音模型最高分，展现出优秀的对话理解与表达能力；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在中英互译任务上， Step-Audio 2 mini 优势明显，在 CoVoST 2 和 CVSS 评测集上分别取得 39.3 和 29.1 的分数，大幅领先 GPT-4o Audio 和其他开源语音模型；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在语音识别任务上，Step-Audio 2 mini 取得多语言和多方言第一。其中开源中文测试集平均 CER（字错误率） 3.19，开源英语测试集平均 WER（词错误率） 3.50，领先其他开源模型 15% 以上。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100002744\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7341597796143251\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1452\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1452\" data-height=\"1066\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"413\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=19b0529c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxzk9FfRXt0XUMRQdWOLavasoMOiboBO0TnibJHMG1T5kEwJDJYIicryNSOxicNz9D54tBuwJlbg9WfgOibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;blockquote&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;editId&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;nickname&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;authorName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;from&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文链接：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(165, 200, 255);\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.16632\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.16632</a></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 40px 8px 32px;text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;\">&nbsp;真端到端架构，轻松听懂“弦外之音”&nbsp;</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">过往的 AI 语音常被吐槽智商、情商双低。一是“没知识”，缺乏文本大模型一样的知识储备和推理能力；二是“冷冰冰”，听不懂潜台词，语气、情绪、笑声这些“弦外之音”。Step-Audio 2 mini 通过创新架构设计，有效解决了此前语音模型存在的问题，做到“走脑又走心”。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">真端到端多模态架构</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：Step-Audio 2 mini 突破传统 ASR+LLM+TTS 三级结构，实现原始音频输入到语音响应输出的直接转换，架构更简洁、时延更低，并能有效理解副语言信息与非人声信号。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100002741\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4861111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"525\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b81a121a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxzk9FfRXt0XUMRQdWOLavasoct8ibVoK4yichhg6lEDz4Nru9UkVfrL6iagCFh6tFWyAQJm7Z2HqbdG4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\">图：Step-Audio 2 mini 模型架构图</span></span></em></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">CoT 推理结合强化学习：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-Audio 2 mini 在端到端语音模型中首次引入链式思维推理（Chain-of-Thought， CoT）与强化学习联合优化，能对情绪、语调、音乐等副语言和非语音信号进行精细理解、推理并自然回应。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">音频知识增强</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型支持包括 web 检索等外部工具，有助于模型解决幻觉问题，并赋予模型在多场景扩展上的能力。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 40px 8px 32px;text-align: center;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 40px 8px 32px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;2 2 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;\">&nbsp;案例分享&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">下面的案例生动地展示了 Step-Audio 2 的能力。无论是大自然的声音、精湛的配音，还是实时信息搜索，它都能精确理解，展现了在处理复杂音频任务上的巨大潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">精准识别，听懂万物之声</span></span></h4>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-Audio 2 mini 像一位听力超棒的音乐家，能分清鸟叫、流水、车声和发条玩具声这四种不同的“音符”。它甚至能听出汽车声中的“激情”——引擎加速和呼啸而过，而不只是冷冰冰地告诉你：“这是车。”</span></span></p>\n  <h4 data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">实时</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">搜索，随时获得行业最新资讯</span></span></strong></h4>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">聊到 OpenAI 最新动态，Step-Audio 2 mini 通过工具调用搜索，迅速挖掘出最新语音模型资讯。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">语速控制，轻松拿捏</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此前，我们发布了同系列满血版 Step Audio 2，现已上线</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">阶跃AI App。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">打开首页，点击右上角“电话”按钮，即可与模型进行实时对话，体验“深度聆听”和“多音色切换”功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">不止对话，一起深度思考</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当被问及“爱美是自由还是枷锁”这类哲学难题时，Step-Audio 2 mini 能将抽象问题转化为“购物前问自己三个问题”的极简方法论。这背后强大的逻辑推理能力，不仅能引导用户厘清思路，更能找到解决问题的具体路径。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 40px 8px 32px;text-align: center;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 40px 8px 32px;text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;2 2 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;\">&nbsp;欢迎体验&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-Audio 2 mini 现已上线阶跃星辰开放平台，欢迎体验和反馈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100002780\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5712484237074401\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1586\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"330\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=78acf7e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznjXuFh1FL7hJ1kOQrOmKyniajs5uwAkO7XcI9PeewMXOZwEq7a7zM93wLXESEoue4flu4zIUZzQ1w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-style: italic;\">体验地址：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(120, 172, 254);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://realtime-console.stepfun.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://realtime-console.stepfun.com</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">点击</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">阅读原文，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">即可跳转模型~</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "阶跃星辰发布开源端到端语音大模型 Step-Audio 2 mini，在语音理解、识别、翻译、情感解析及对话等任务中性能卓越，超越主流模型，并支持原生 Tool Calling。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阶跃星辰发布开源端到端语音大模型 Step-Audio 2 mini，在语音理解、识别、翻译、情感解析及对话等任务中性能卓越，超越主流模型，并支持原生 Tool Calling。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了阶跃星辰最新发布的开源端到端语音大模型 Step-Audio 2 mini。该模型在音频理解、语音识别、跨语种翻译、情感解析和语音对话等多个任务中均取得 SOTA（State-Of-The-Art）成绩，综合性能超越了包括 Qwen-Omni、Kimi-Audio 在内的所有开源端到端语音模型，并在大部分任务上超越了 GPT-4o Audio。Step-Audio 2 mini 采用真端到端多模态架构，突破传统 ASR+LLM+TTS 三级结构，实现了原始音频输入到语音响应输出的直接转换，有效理解副语言信息。其主要创新点在于，作为端到端语音模型的首次尝试，它引入了链式思维推理（CoT）与强化学习（RL）联合优化，并支持原生 Tool Calling 能力，可进行联网搜索。模型已在 GitHub、Hugging Face 和 ModelScope 等平台开源，并提供了体验链接。",
